-- Japan Says Public Debt to Reach 985.4 Trillion Yen in FY 2011
-- B y   M a y u m i   O t s u m a
-- 2012-01-24T10:05:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/japan-says-public-debt-to-reach-985-4-trillion-yen-in-fy-2011.html
Japan ’s  Finance Ministry  said the
nation’s public debt will probably reach 985.4 trillion yen
($12.7 trillion) in the year ending March 2012, up 6.6 percent
from a year earlier, according to a statement released in  Tokyo 
today. The figure reflected adjustments in a fourth extra
budget.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mayumi Otsuma in Tokyo at 
 motsuma@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
